title: The Hangover 1, 2 & 3
description:
The Hangover (2009) DVD Rip

A Las Vegas-set comedy centered around three groomsmen who lose their about-to-be-wed buddy during their drunken misadventures, then must retrace their steps in order to find him.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Hangover Part II (2011) DVD Rip

Two years after the bachelor party in Las Vegas, Phil, Stu, Alan, and Doug jet to Thailand for Stu's wedding. Stu's plan for a subdued pre-wedding brunch, however, goes seriously awry.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Hangover Part III (2013) Cam copy (decent quality though and audio is synced)

When one of their own is kidnapped by an angry gangster, the Wolf Pack must track down Mr. Chow, who has escaped from prison and is on the lam.
